attributionInfo.brokerName: All City Real Estate Ltd. Co

data.description:
This beautiful and lovingly maintained 3BR, 2BA brick home is for sale!  Located within walking distance of Parsons/Clements Elementary school, makes this home highly desirable. Two dining areas, and a large living room with a fireplace makes entertaining friends and family easy! Beautiful flooring throughout the home adds to the appeal.  
The large backyard surrounded by a wooden fence is perfect for the children and the family fur babies.
Call your favorite realtor today to see this lovely home!
